title: Monty Python - The Autobiography
description:
Audio Books : Humor : MP3/Over 256Kbps : English


by Michael Palin (Author), John Cleese (Author), Terry Gilliam (Author), Eric Idle (Author), Terry Jones (Author), Bob McCabe (Author)

This is the Audio Book companion to the big hunking 365 page book by the same name. The audio book consists of well over two hours of audio interviews of the surviving Pythons. These stories were the basis of many of the sections in the book. As such it certainly isn't unabbridged as it isn't a reading of or even from the book. It is also not abbridged as there are comments made that didn't make it into the book... think of it as acompanion to the book, if that makes sense.
